. In the tab 'Menu Assignment' make sure that the module is displayed on all pages. At the end click the button <code class=\"language-text\">Save</code> in the toolbar.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/191e2/j4x36x2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.10126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Create Joomla Module\"\n        title=\"Create Joomla Module\"\n        src=\"/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/f058b/j4x36x2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/c26ae/j4x36x2.png 158w,\n/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/6bdcf/j4x36x2.png 315w,\n/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/f058b/j4x36x2.png 630w,\n/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/40601/j4x36x2.png 945w,\n/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/78612/j4x36x2.png 1260w,\n/static/5c312f9bedc7d240379c87367b682d47/191e2/j4x36x2.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>That's it. Switch to the frontend view and make sure that everything is displayed correctly.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    hre